      "content": "hey i need to talk to someone about something weird. i think i'm seeing things... or not seeing them the way everyone else does? like i saw this specific cracked blue vase in a shop window today and it felt so heavy, like it was pulsing. then literally two hours later i saw a headline about a massive explosion at a glass factory. it felt like the vase was showing me what was gonna happen. am i losing it??",
